  "synopsis": "He's bald. He's bad. His lightsaber is purple. He's MACE WINDU! Make sure not to miss out on this stunning tribute to the baddest Jedi Council member to ever have his midiclorians counted! Featuring \"The Secret of Tet-Ami\" by Fabian Nicieza and Timothy II, \"Children of the Force\" by Jason Hall and Lucas Marangon, \"The Sith in Shadow\" by Bob Harris and Jerome Opena, and MUCH MORE! Featuring a cover by Tim Bradstreet!",
